Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉嶺紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿薩姆紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這家店裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都能夠看到客人高興的臉龐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗滋莉小姐的紅茶真是好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝...呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是兩位客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請裡面坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
