Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎...怎麼回事  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大喊「啊 討厭」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是「不分青紅皂白的馬上給你一巴掌」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要選哪種 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩兩兩  兩種都不必
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也還想要一戰 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有想和你們戰鬥的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能夠來證明 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是那個代代都是擔任鬼斬役的人 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰又能夠來證明 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是那個代代都擔任鬼斬役的人 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拿什麼來證明 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 天河優人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 斬鬼役 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想跟緋鞠和凜子她們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像之前...一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少...少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人 走吧　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起就可以過普普通通的生活了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...在浴室...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候穿好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒看見 沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩人可是看的一清二楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又...又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們還說「真是大飽眼福」 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色情狂 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 快退下  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這類妖魔如果不親身嘗一次苦頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會得到教訓的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 緋鞠 冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你們之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越覺得有著要和你們戰鬥的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會讓人感到很蠢 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以早就說過我們根本沒有戰鬥的意願嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼天真的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止 好好看清現實吧 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為您著想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的為我著想的話  就更要把劍收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然流著鼻涕哭起來了 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人對貓過敏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過敏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的說就是出現類似身體拒絕的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當痛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要身邊有貓的話就很痛苦的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身體就會抗拒的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要特意待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是越來越弄不明白的傢伙 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河優人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜水久 我確實不能舉出任何證據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我沒有那麼懂事到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為是妖怪或鬼斬役 就要相互廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和緋鞠她們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像現在這樣子平靜的生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我並不想和被鬼斬役奪取平靜生活的靜水久戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你不會相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主太過善良了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要馬上得知你的回答 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你能理解真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對對  只要能了解優人的話 就不會有所誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留在這裡並和你一起住的話 就能更加的了解你 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊（石化）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教  的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 這是靜水久做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享用 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊嗚  嗯嗯 太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種敗北感是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎沒有加什麼可疑的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 這種話早該在剛才就說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是停戰期間 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我稍稍修行一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩三天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一周  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一個月之內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你要去哪兒 緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯也吃過了 那我就去洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個的話我剛才就洗好了 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就打掃...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打掃完了 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還...還有點能耐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊    
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緋鞠她 鬧彆扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊   
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這時候去擔心貓要幹嘛阿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是會做這些的話 都可以當合格的新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊    
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 今宵我就像優人期待的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地服侍你 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊  優人   
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你千萬不要接受這種邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的就好 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那樣了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 不行嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶...靜水久很擅長家務事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鬼斬役出現之前  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起戰鬥 有點像這樣生活本領是相當重要的 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這男人所嚮往的平凡生活當中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了會戰鬥以外什麼都不會的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠給與他什麼 的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼態度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是稍稍會做點家事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個守護者也是有身為守護者的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊 野井原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
